    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape, super reliable, and has been really well-loved over the years. The interior is nice and clean, and it still handles like a dream on the road. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks sharp and is ready for its next adventure, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
