    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. This example retains its tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is well-sorted, with recent inspections of the rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive VANOS system service to ensure variable valve timing remains within factory tolerances. It features a firm suspension geometry with crisp turn-in, riding on staggered alloy wheels. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain is robust and the performance envelope remains sharp. A true driver's car for those who prioritize mechanical integrity and analog feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
