    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and serves as a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only the minor road chips one would expect from careful use, and the body panels are straight and true. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the leather bolsters show minimal softening, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust and reliable. It comes with a comprehensive service history, including recent fluid changes, a new battery, and a fresh set of high-performance tires with significant tread remaining. The engine pulls smoothly across the rev range, and the transmission shifts are crisp and certain. This is a turn-key car that perfectly balances luxury and performance for a buyer who values maintenance and peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
