      "description": "This impeccably maintained vehicle represents a premier selection for the sophisticated driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical reliability and a refined aesthetic presence, it has been curated to ensure a superior experience on the road. With a focus on structural integrity and performance longevity, this offering stands as a testament to diligent ownership and professional standards. A distinguished choice for those who demand quality and value in a pre-owned executive vehicle.",
      "price": 36500.0,
