    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride that's ready to hit the road? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can count on it for all your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It runs smoothly and looks great\u2014honestly, it's just a fantastic, dependable vehicle looking for its next home. Come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself! I\u2019m happy to answer any questions you have.",
      "price": 32500.0,
