    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term chassis rigidity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a cooling system overhaul. While the aesthetic reflects its status as an enjoyed driver's car, the mechanical vitals are sharp, offering the tactile feedback and 8,000 RPM linear power delivery that defines this era of M-performance.",
